title.rendered: McAfee LiveSafe, for PC, Apple Mac, iOS, or Android, Unlimited Devices, 1-Year Subscription, eCard

content.rendered:
Ultimate antivirus, identity and privacy protection for all your PCs, Macs, smartphones and tablets
Award-winning internet security Over 500 million protected devices and counting.
Secure WiFi On-the-go Secure Wi-Fi Keep your browsing habits and data safe from prying eyes when connected to public Wi-Fi.
Cross-device protection Protect your PCs, Macs, smartphones, and tablets with one subscription.
Antivirus protection and much more, covering your computers, mobile devices and even your identity.
